                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-194-off1034 t18190915-194-cd1035"></join>, one table-cloth, value 5 s.; one table-cover, value 2 s.; one pair of drawers, value 6 d., and one gown, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190915-194-victim1679" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Brightwen
                  <interp inst="t18190915-194-victim1679" type="surname" value="Brightwen"></interp>
